item.title: Golden State Warriors Unveil 2024-25 Statement Edition Uniforms, New Secondary Logo
item.description: The Golden State Warriors unveiled their 2024-25 Statement Edition uniforms, as well as their new secondary logo, which is prominently displayed on the shorts.

item.title: Oregon Ducks Unveil Black “Generation O” Football Uniforms
item.description: Oregon unveiled the first combination of its new “Generation O” uniforms on Wednesday afternoon with an all-black option that blends various elements from the Ducks’ previous designs.
